#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/docs/books/admin_guide/03-commands.md:1462
#, no-wrap
msgid "The `alias` command lists the aliases for the current session. Aliases are set by default on Linux distributions. Here, the aliases for a Rocky server:\n"
